ucts to a select group to review and receive rewards.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Read on to learn more about how to apply and what you can earn.</span><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Applications open from now until Sunday September 11, 23:59.</strong></p><p><strong><br></strong></p></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662384403793" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662384403793" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662386857561" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662386857561"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><strong>1. What product will you be reviewing?</strong></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662385975776" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662385975776"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">The <span style="font-weight: bold;">MARY & MAY CICA Soothing Sun Cream SPF50+ PA++++</span> is a multifunctional, reef-friendly sun cream that moisturizes and soothes skin and offers skin-brightening & anti-aging effects.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">It’s fitted with SPF 50+ PA++++ for UV protection and formulated with 10,000ppm of F-CICA COMPLEX (containing seven centella asiatica derivatives fermented with yeast) for soothing effects.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Sun cream’s lightweight texture absorbs quickly into skin without leaving a white cast.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Click <span style="color: rgb(124, 175, 104);">here</span> to read more about this product.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662368850360" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662368850360" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/products/mary-may-cica-soothing-sun-cream-spf50-pa?variant=39680721322047" target="_blank"><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/a0d0a9fb-93ec-4308-b3e7-51243c115bc6/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Mary-&-May---Sunscreen.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="800" height="800" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="800" natural-height="800"></a></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662382536745" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662382536745"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b>2. WHAT CAN YOU EARN?</b></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1653395842692" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1653395842692"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Every person selected to participate in this event will receive all of the perks listed below!</span><br></p><p><strong><br></strong></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653395842649" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1653395842649" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-md" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/88554f80-60ba-499a-9ccc-720c89b43c5d/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Benifits.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1465" height="533" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1465" natural-height="533"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662386553832" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662386553832"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><b style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">3. WHAT WILL THE BEST REVIEW WIN?</b><br></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1653395842735" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1653395842735"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc="">In honor of our very first KS Review Event, the KS Team will be choosing <span style="font-weight: bold;">1 special winner</span> for best review. &nbsp;<span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">The winner will receive all of the previous benefits along with extra KS Points and a free surprise gift in their next purchase.&nbsp;</span><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></div></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1653395842608" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1653395842608" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-md" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/ebc49219-6dd2-4d33-841e-d2f41c124bdc/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Best-Review.jpg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1465" height="533" data-width="80%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1465" natural-height="533"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662386588736" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662386588736"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><b style="letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;">4. HOW WILL THE KS TEAM CHOOSE BEST REVIEW?</b><br></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662387448367" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662387448367"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">For the Best Review, the KS Team is looking for:</span><div><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• excellent quality</span></div><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• informative content</span></div><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• honest feelings</span></div><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">• constructive feedback</span></div><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);"><br></span></div><div><span style="font-family: var(--fonts_name),&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; letter-spacing: 0px; background-color: var(--body_bg);">Therefore, your review does <span style="font-weight: bold;">not</span> need to be positive to be considered for this award. We will judge the review based on which one we believe is the most helpful to other customers in aiding them to assess whether this product is a good fit for them.&nbsp;</span></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662386753027" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662386753027" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-cente