gn="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662386545249" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662386545249"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><div>We cannot wait to send you guys these new products and see the fun reviews you create.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Wishing you all the best of luck!</div><div><br></div><div>Love,&nbsp;</div><div>KS Team</div><div><br></div></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1662388268037" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1662388268037" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662381679454" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662381679454"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b>TERMS & CONDITIONS</b></p></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1662383035923" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1662383035923"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>1. The KS Team reserves the right to choose who will participate in this event.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Only those who apply directly on the Review Event announcement TikTok via comment will be considered. Those who apply via TikTok DMs, Instagram, Facebook, or email will not be considered.</p><p>3. Only those who fulfill ALL of the requirements to apply will be considered.</p><p>4. If chosen, you will be notified on September 13 via TikTok DM from our official TikTok account. Failure to reply by September 14th at 12:00 CET will result in you losing your spot and another person will be chosen to replace you.</p><p>5. By agreeing to participate, you are agreeing to receive a free product in exchange for posting a review to your public TikTok account by October 7, 2022.</p><p>6. Do not apply if you live outside of Korean Skincare's <a href="https://koreanskincare.nl/pages/send-information" class="">shipping range</a>.&nbsp;</p><p>7. Do not apply if you are not willing to make your TikTok account public.&nbsp;</p><p>8. Once your TikTok deliverable is confirmed to be delivered by October 7, 2022, the KS Team will present your rewards by October 11, 2022.&nbsp;</p><p>9. The KS Team reserves the right to withhold rewards from anybody who does not fulfill their tasks by the assigned deadline.</p><p>10. Korean Skincare reserves the right to utilize any content created for this event. Content can be reposted to any Korean Skincare media.</p></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><script>window.__gemStoreData = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid = {};window.__gemStoreData.gemKeyValid.bestWayAddToCart = 1;</script></div><div id="divContentBk"></div><!--End_Gem_Page_Main_Editor-->
